library\"},\"align\":\"center\",\"width\":{\"unit\":\"%\",\"size\":100,\"sizes\":[]},\"_padding\":{\"unit\":\"%\",\"top\":\"7\",\"right\":\"7\",\"bottom\":\"7\",\"left\":\"7\",\"isLinked\":true},\"_padding_tablet\":{\"unit\":\"%\",\"top\":\"\",\"right\":\"\",\"bottom\":\"\",\"left\":\"\",\"isLinked\":true},\"_padding_mobile\":{\"unit\":\"%\",\"top\":\"\",\"right\":\"\",\"bottom\":\"\",\"left\":\"\",\"isLinked\":true},\"height\":{\"unit\":\"px\",\"size\":223,\"sizes\":[]}},\"elements\":[],\"widgetType\":\"image\"}],\"isInner\":true},{\"id\":\"3945dfb\",\"elType\":\"container\",\"settings\":{\"flex_direction\":\"column\",\"content_width\":\"full\",\"width\":{\"unit\":\"%\",\"size\":24.51},\"_flex_size\":\"none\",\"_element_width\":\"initial\"},\"elements\":[{\"id\":\"f43a567\",\"elType\":\"widget\",\"settings\":{\"image\":{\"url\":\"http:\\/\\/localhost\\/fundacion_angel_peludos\\/wp-content\\/uploads\\/2024\\/03\\/davi.jpeg\",\"id\":317,\"size\":\"\",\"alt\":\"\",\"source\":\"library\"},\"align\":\"center\",\"width\":{\"unit\":\"%\",\"size\":51,\"sizes\":[]}},\"elements\":[],\"widgetType\":\"image\"},{\"id\":\"eb5fc64\",\"elType\":\"widget\",\"settings\":{\"editor\":\"<p>3157405569<\\/p>\",\"align\":\"center\"},\"elements\":[],\"widgetType\":\"text-editor\"},{\"id\":\"70aadfd\",\"elType\":\"widget\",\"settings\":{\"image\":{\"url\":\"http:\\/\\/localhost\\/fundacion_angel_peludos\\/wp-content\\/uploads\\/2024\\/03\\/QR.jpeg\",\"id\":320,\"size\":\"\",\"alt\":\"\",\"source\":\"library\"},\"align\":\"center\",\"width\":{\"unit\":\"%\",\"size\":100,\"sizes\":[]},\"height\":{\"unit\":\"px\",\"size\":140,\"sizes\":[]},\"_margin\":{\"unit\":\"px\",\"top\":\"0\",\"right\":\"0\",\"bottom\":\"0\",\"left\":\"0\",\"isLinked\":true},\"_padding\":{\"unit\":\"px\",\"top\":\"71\",\"right\":\"71\",\"bottom\":\"71\",\"left\":\"71\",\"isLinked\":true}},\"elements\":[],\"widgetType\":\"image\"}],\"isInner\":true}],\"isInner\":false},{\"id\":\"114356f\",\"elType\":\"container\",\"settings\":{\"flex_direction\":\"column\"},\"elements\":[{\"id\":\"2bdefa7\",\"elType\":\"widget\",\"settings\":{\"editor\":\"<p><strong>Voluntariado:<\\/strong> \\u00danete a nuestro equipo como voluntario y s\\u00e9 parte de nuestra misi\\u00f3n. Ya sea ayudando en eventos de adopci\\u00f3n, cuidando a los animales en nuestro refugio o brindando apoyo administrativo, tu tiempo y dedicaci\\u00f3n son invaluables para nosotros.<\\/p><p><strong>Adopciones Responsables:<\\/strong> Considera abrir tu hogar y coraz\\u00f3n a una mascota necesitada. Adoptar un animal de nuestra fundaci\\u00f3n no solo cambia la vida del animal, sino que tambi\\u00e9n enriquece la tuya. \\u00a1Convi\\u00e9rtete en un h\\u00e9roe adoptando a un compa\\u00f1ero peludo hoy!<\\/p><p><strong>Compartir en Redes Sociales:<\\/strong> Ay\\u00fadanos a difundir nuestra misi\\u00f3n compartiendo nuestras publicaciones en redes sociales. Cuanto m\\u00e1s alcance tengamos, m\\u00e1s personas podremos inspirar para unirse a nuestra causa y ayudar a las mascotas necesitadas.<\\/p>\",\"align\":\"justify\",\"_margin\":{\"unit\":\"px\",\"top\":\"0\",\"right\":\"0\",\"bottom\":\"0\",\"left\":\"0\",\"isLinked\":true},\"_padding\":{\"unit\":\"px\",\"top\":\"0\",\"right\":\"0\",\"bottom\":\"0\",\"left\":\"0\",\"isLinked\":true},\"_element_width\":\"initial\",\"_element_custom_width\":{\"unit\":\"%\",\"size\":80},\"_flex_size\":\"none\"},\"elements\":[],\"widgetType\":\"text-editor\"}],\"isInner\":false},{\"id\":\"f530827\",\"elType\":\"container\",\"settings\":{\"flex_direction\":\"column\"},\"elements\":[{\"id\":\"9ee8809\",\"elType\":\"widget\",\"settings\":{\"editor\":\"<p><strong>Haz la Diferencia Hoy<\\/strong><\\/p><p>Tu apoyo es esencial para el \\u00e9xito de nuestra misi\\u00f3n. \\u00a1Juntos, podemos marcar la diferencia en la vida de los animales necesitados y trabajar hacia un futuro donde todas las mascotas sean amadas, respetadas y cuidadas!<\\/p><p><strong>\\u00bfListo para Apoyarnos?<\\/strong><\\/p><p>Si est\\u00e1s interesado en apoyar nuestra causa o deseas obtener m\\u00e1s informaci\\u00f3n sobre c\\u00f3mo puedes involucrarte, \\u00a1cont\\u00e1ctanos hoy mismo! Tu apoyo significa el mundo para nosotros y para las mascotas que ayudamos.<\\/p>\",\"align\":\"justify\",\"_element_width\":\"initial\",\"_element_custom_width\":{\"unit\":\"%\",\"size\":80},\"_flex_size\":\"none\"},\"elements\":[],\"widgetType\":\"text-editor\"},{\"id\":\"cf26a42\",\"elType\":\"widget\",\"settings\":{\"image\":{\"url\":\"http:\\/\\/localhost\\/fundacion_angel_peludos\\/wp-content\\/uploads\\/2024\\/03\\/contac.jpeg\",\"id\":316,\"size\":\"\",\"alt\":\"\",\"source\":\"library\"},\"align\":\"center\",\"hover_animation\":\"bob\",\"image_border_radius\":{\"unit\":\"%\",\"top\":\"100\",\"right\":\"100\",\"bottom\":\"100\",\"left\":\"100\",\"isLinked\":true},\"image_border_radius_tablet\":{\"unit\":\"%\",\"top\":\"\",\"right\":\"\",\"bottom\":\"\",\"left\":\"\",\"isLinked\":true},\"image_border_radius_mobile\":{\"unit\":\"%\",\"top\":\"\",\"right\":\"\",\"bottom\":\"\",\"left\":\"\",\"isLinked\":true},\"link_to\":\"custom\",\"link\":{\"url\":\"http:\\/\\/localhost\\/fundacion_angel_peludos\\/formularios\\/formularioCon.php\",\"is_external\":\"\",\"nofollow\":\"\",\"custom_attributes\":\"\"}},\"elements\":[],\"widgetType\":\"image\"},{\"id\":\"b9c928a\",\"elType\":\"widget\",\"settings\":{\"editor\":\"<p><span style=\\\"text-decoration: underline;\\\"><em><strong>Dale click encima al perrito para contactarnos<\\/strong><\\/em><\\/span><\\/p>\",\"text_color\":\"#1215AF\",\"align\":\"center\"},\"elements\":[],\"widgetType\":\"text-editor\"}],\"isInner\":false}]'),
